Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻 综合报道今天，福建泉州相关部门召开新闻发布会。
Peng Pai news comprehensive report today, Fujian Quanzhou related departments held a press conference.
泉州市政府常务副市长洪自强在会上表示：事发坍塌建筑建设于2013年，主体7层，为钢结构建筑物。
Quanzhou City Deputy Mayor Hong Zhiqiang said at the meeting: the incident collapsed in 2013, the main seventh floor, steel structure buildings.
酒店有各类客房共计66间。
The hotel has a total of 66 rooms.
已成立事故调查组，该楼房业主已被公安部门控制。
An accident investigation team has been set up and the owner of the building is under public security control.
据@应急管理部最新消息，福建省泉州市欣佳酒店“3·7”房屋坍塌事故现场共有71人被困（不含自救逃生的9人）。
A total of 71 people were stranded at the site of the March 7 collapse at the Xinjia Hotel in Quanzhou City, Fujian Province, according to the latest news from @ Ministry of Emergency Management.
截至3月8日16时，已救出48人（其中10人死亡，38人送医治疗），正在搜救的还有23人。
As at 1600 hours on 8 March, 48 people had been rescued (10 killed and 38 treated) and 23 others were in search and rescue.
男童获救出来后说的第一句话“妈妈在我下面，还活着”据@中国消防消息，11时24分，消防员成功将一名12岁的小男孩救出，孩子第一句话是“妈妈在我下面，还活着”。
A firefighter rescued a 12-year-old boy at 11: 24 a.m. with the child's first line saying, "Mom is alive under me," according to China Fire News.
Play视频来源：@中国消防据@福建消防消息，13时14分，男孩的妈妈上半身已经出来了，部分身体还被卡住，消防救援人员给她喂水。
Play video source: @ China Firefighting @ Fujian Fire News, 13: 14, the boy's mother has come out of the upper body, part of the body is still stuck, fire rescue personnel to feed her water.
13时26分，消防救援人员通过蛇眼生命探测仪进行探测，发现男孩的妈妈的小腿部位被角铁卡住了，现在正在想办法解救。
At 1326 hours, firefighters using the Snake Eyes Life Detector discovered that the boy's mother's calf was stuck in a corner iron and was trying to find a way out.
男子获救时指着妻孩的方向反复强调他们的位置据福建消防，8日8点13分，厦门市消防救援支队救出一名被困男子，他的妻子和孩子还被压在底下，救援正在进行。
Rescue workers in Xiamen at 8: 13 am rescued a trapped man, his wife and children were still trapped, and rescue work is under way, according to the Fujian fire department.
据央视新闻，男子获救时指着妻孩的方向，反复向消防员强调他们的位置。
When rescued, the man pointed to his wife and child and repeatedly stressed their position to firefighters, CCTV said.
Play视频来源：央视新闻下午两点，厦门市消防救援人员救出一名男孩，是该男子的儿子。
Rescue workers in Xiamen rescued a boy, the man's son, at 2 pm on CCTV news.
（本文综合自澎湃新闻、@应急管理部、@央视新闻、@中国消防、@福建消防）救援还在继续愿尽快救出所有被困者！本期编辑邢潭推荐阅读。
(This article is a combination of Pai Pai News, @ Emergency Management Department, @ CCTV News, @ China Fire Protection, @ Fujian Fire Protection) Rescue efforts continue and all those trapped continue to be rescued as soon as possible!
